OL,3,CDrone footage shows train line upgrade
OL,4,Cworks over Easter Weekend
OL,6,FWatch drone footage of Carnforth
OL,7,Fsignalling gantry renewals.JCredit:
OL,8,FNetwork Rail
OL,10,FDrone footage has pulled back the
OL,11,Fcurtain on the multi-million-pound
OL,12,Fprojects which took place on the West
OL,13,FCoast Main Line over the Easter
OL,14,Fweekend.
OL,16,FNetwork Rail teams had to cope with
OL,17,FStorm Dave during the construction,
OL,18,Fwhich brought gale force winds and
OL,19,Fheavy rain.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
