OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1775555970
OL,3,CDrone footage shows train line upgrade
OL,4,Cworks over Easter Weekend
OL,6,FOverhead power lines were upgraded and
OL,7,Fmodern LED signal lamps were installed
OL,8,Fas part of the works.
OL,10,FThe West Coast Main Line was reopened
OL,11,Fon Easter Monday between Preston and
OL,12,FOxenholme, after two days of closure
OL,13,Fwhich saw trains using the historic
OL,14,FSettle-Carlisle line as a diversion.
OL,16,F#400million is currently being
OL,17,Finvested into the train line, which
OL,18,Fconnects London to Manchester,
OL,19,FCarlisle, and cities even further
OL,20,Fafield.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
