FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1775555970
OL,3,CDrone footage shows train line upgrade
OL,4,Cworks over Easter Weekend
OL,6,FBetween Saturday April 11 and Sunday
OL,7,FApril 19 the northern section of the
OL,8,FWest Coast line will close again,
OL,9,Fbetween Preston, Lancaster and Fylde,
OL,10,Fbringing more disruption for commuters
OL,11,Fwanting to travel south of Carlisle.
OL,13,FThe Settle to Carlisle line will be
OL,14,Fbrought into service as a diversionary
OL,15,Froute, while replacement buses will
OL,16,Falso run.
OL,18,FThis is to allow for overhead power
OL,19,Fline renewals.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
