PN,35204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1775555970
OL,3,CDrone footage shows train line upgrade
OL,4,Cworks over Easter Weekend
OL,6,FChristian Irwin OBE, Network Rail
OL,7,FNorth West and Central region Capital
OL,8,FDelivery director, said: "I'd like to
OL,9,Fthank passengers for their patience
OL,10,Fwhile we've been carrying out these
OL,11,Fmajor railway upgrades to improve
OL,12,Fjourneys in the North West this Easter.
OL,14,F"Despite Storm Dave we were able to
OL,15,Fuse the extended bank holiday to get
OL,16,Fstarted with some really important
OL,17,Fprojects as part of our significant
OL,18,Fupgrade plan to the West Coast Main
OL,19,FLine.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
